\begin_layout Section
S矩阵元的洛伦兹不变性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如同本章开头提到的，
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

–矩阵元的洛伦兹不变性是自旋–统计定理的足够条件。
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

–矩阵元是由编时乘积构成的，最简单的非平庸编时乘积就是费曼传播子。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
必须对玻色子和费米子定义编时乘积。费米子产生和湮灭算符在通常的动量和时间是反对易的，所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T\left\{ a_{p}\left(t\right)a_{q}\left(t^{\prime}\right)\right\} =-T\left\{ a_{q}\left(t^{\prime}\right)a_{p}\left(t\right)\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

因此，对于费米子，我们除了按时间排序，还要跟踪负号。不然上面的式子意味着编时乘积等于零。因此，对于由费米子产生湮灭算符组成的一般函数
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

，唯一自洽的编时乘积定义 是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T\left\{ \psi\left(x\right)\chi\left(y\right)\right\} =\theta\left(x^{0}-y^{0}\right)\psi\left(x\right)\chi\left(y\right)-\theta\left(y^{0}-x^{0}\right)\chi\left(y\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

现在我们可以考虑费米子的编时乘积了。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
自旋0
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们先来复习一下复标量场的情况。场和它的复共轭的真空矩阵元是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}\phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\frac{\dd^{3}q}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{p}}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{q}}}\bra{0}\left(a_{p}^{+}e^{ipx}+b_{p}e^{-ipx}\right)\left(a_{q}+b_{q}^{\dagger}\right)\ket{0}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{-i\omega_{p}t+i\vec{p}\vec{x}}=\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{-ipx}\text{ 传播反粒子}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

类似地，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}\phi\left(0\right)\phi^{*}\left(x\right)\ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\frac{\dd^{3}q}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{p}}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{q}}}\bra{0}\left(a_{q}+b_{q}^{\dagger}\right)\left(a_{p}^{+}e^{ipx}+b_{p}e^{-ipx}\right)\ket{0}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{i\omega_{p}t-i\vec{p}\vec{x}}=\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{ipx}\text{ 传播粒子}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

将这两个方程结合，我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0}=\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}\left[e^{i\vec{p}\vec{x}-i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(t\right)+e^{-i\vec{p}\vec{x}+i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(-t\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset

在第一项中令
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}\to-\vec{p}$
\end_inset

，积分测度联合积分区域整体不变，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0}=\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{-i\vec{p}\vec{x}}\left[e^{-i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(t\right)+e^{+i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(-t\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset

使用 eq.6.30 and 6.31
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
e^{+i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(-t\right) & =\frac{i}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dd\omega}{\omega-\left(\omega_{p}-i\varepsilon\right)}e^{i\omega t}\text{ 第四象限\ensuremath{t<0}才有值}\\
e^{-i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(t\right) & =-\frac{i}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dd\omega}{\omega-\left(-\omega_{p}+i\varepsilon\right)}e^{i\omega t}\text{ 第二象限\ensuremath{t>0}才有值}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{2\omega_{p}}e^{ipx}\left(\frac{1}{\omega-\left(\omega_{p}-i\varepsilon\right)}-\frac{1}{\omega+\left(\omega_{p}-i\varepsilon\right)}\right)\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{2\omega_{p}}e^{ipx}\left(\frac{2\omega_{p}}{\omega^{2}-\omega_{p}^{2}+i\varepsilon}\right)\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{\omega^{2}-\omega_{p}^{2}+i\varepsilon}e^{ipx}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}e^{ipx}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $p^{0}\equiv\omega$
\end_inset

是积分变量。这个结果是洛伦兹不变的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果我们用反对易关系，我们需要用反对易编时乘积，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}e^{-i\vec{p}\vec{x}}\left[e^{-i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(t\right)-e^{+i\omega_{p}t}\theta\left(-t\right)\right]\\
 & =-\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{2\omega_{p}}e^{ipx}\left(\frac{1}{\omega-\left(\omega_{p}-i\varepsilon\right)}+\frac{1}{\omega+\left(\omega_{p}-i\varepsilon\right)}\right)\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{-p^{0}}{\sqrt{\vec{p}^{2}+m^{2}}}\frac{i}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}e^{ipx}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

它不是洛伦兹不变的。所以只有当自旋–
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

粒子是玻色子，它的
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

–矩阵元才是洛伦兹不变的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
此外，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi\left(x\right)\phi^{*}\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0} & =\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi^{*}\left(x\right)\phi\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}\left[e^{-ipx}\theta\left(t\right)+e^{+ipx}\theta\left(-t\right)\right]=\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}e^{-ipx}\\
\bra{0}T\left\{ \phi\left(x\right)\phi^{*}\left(0\right)\right\} \ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}\left[e^{-ipx}\theta\left(t\right)+e^{+ipx}\theta\left(-t\right)\right]=\int\frac{\dd^{4}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{i}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}e^{-ipx}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

也就是说，标量场传播子对于动量是偶函数，传播子的数值是一样的。不过传播的粒子刚好反过来。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
费米子
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在我们对旋量重复计算。开头一样：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\bra{0}\psi\left(0\right)\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\ket{0} & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\frac{\dd^{3}q}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{p}}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{q}}}\sum_{s,s^{\prime}}\bra{0}\left(a_{p}^{s}u_{p}^{s}+b_{p}^{s\dagger}v_{p}^{s}\right)\left(a_{q}^{s^{\prime}\dagger}\bar{u}_{q}^{s^{\prime}}e^{iqx}+b_{q}^{s^{\prime}}\bar{v}_{q}^{s^{\prime}}e^{-iqx}\right)\ket{0}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\frac{\dd^{3}q}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{p}}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\omega_{q}}}\sum_{s,s^{\prime}}u_{p}^{s}\bar{u}_{q}^{s^{\prime}}\bra{0}a_{p}^{s}a_{q}^{s^{\prime}\dagger}\ket{0}e^{iqx}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{3}p}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{1}{2\omega_{p}}\sum_{s}u_{p}^{s}\bar{u}_{p}^{s}e^{ipx}\text{ 传播正粒子}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

注意
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\left(0\right)\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

的意思是旋量空间的矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula $\bra{0}\psi\left(0\right)_{\alpha}\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)_{\beta}\ket{0}\sim\left(u_{p}^{s}\right)_{\alpha}\left(\bar{u}_{p}^{s}\right)_{\beta}$
